data.description: This charming, classic home is ready for new owners! The spacious living room and kitchen is perfect for cooking and entertaining, with the added bonus of a formal dining area. Enjoy the best of both worlds - defined spaces that also offer open concept design! The Primary Suite and secondary bedrooms are large with lots of natural light. The flooring has been updated (no carpet!), and the walls feature light neutral colors so that you can decorate however you like. Located on a quiet street, conveniently near I-10 and Garth Rd for an easy commute. Schedule your tour and fall in love!
